org.apache.axis2.jaxws.marshaller
Class MethodParameter

java.lang.Object
  org.apache.axis2.jaxws.marshaller.MethodParameter

public class MethodParameter
extends Object

Stores Method Parameter as Name and Value. Method Parameter can be an input Method Parameter or output Method parameter. input Method Parameter is a input to a java Method. output Method Parameter is a return parameter from a java Method.
